channel.description:
[u][size=36pt]Project Utopia[/size][/u] It's time to release this. A little project of mine for the last few week or months. Added quite a few new things.
[ul][li]New home[/li] [li]Skillcape emotes[/li] [li]Client was updated[/li] [li]Background all fixed up[/li] [li]Lots more but I CBA to post them all here[/li][/ul]
[img]http://img684.imageshack.us/img684/1014/homete.png[/img] [img]http://img228.imageshack.us/img228/1526/projecta.png[/img]
